{"id":432213,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2016/03/432213/","date":"2016-03-19T08:18:46Z","modified":"2016-03-19T08:18:46Z","title":"【立此存照】帝吧出征维珍航空 认错公司无辜躺枪","content":"<p>近日，一名中国女性乘客自称在维珍航空(Virgin Atlantic)从伦敦飞往上海的航班中遭到一位白人男性乘客的辱骂，更<a href=\"http://weibo.com/p/1001603954310793809448\" target=\"_blank\">指对方种族歧视</a>，使用了如“中国猪”这样的语言。</p>\n<p>此事件在网络<a href=\"http://www.guancha.cn/europe/2016_03_19_354395.shtml\" target=\"_blank\">持续发酵</a>。维珍航空官方账号在微博对此事进行了回应，称将彻查此事。维珍航空公司总裁也随后在网络上<a href=\"https://www.virgin.com/richard-branson/social-media-and-understanding-all-sides-story\" target=\"_blank\">公开回应</a>，强调了该司对种族歧视零容忍，同时表示需要彻查后才能给出结论。</p>\n<p>许多中国网民很显然无法接受该总裁没有道歉的事实。于是出现了最近的帝吧“出征维珍航空FB页面”行动，要逼其道歉。</p>\n<p>然而由于维珍集团旗下拥有大量子公司，航空方面除Virgin Atlantic外，还有同样独立运作的Virgin America和Virgin Australia。这直接导致了许多“不明真相”的热血网民跑去Virgin America、Virgin Australia以及维珍集团总部的Facebook页面开骂。</p>\n<p><strong>躺枪的Virgin America脸书页面：</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/03/virgin-america1.png\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-432217\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-432217\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/03/virgin-america1.png\" alt=\"virgin america1\" width=\"425\" height=\"720\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/03/virgin-america1.png 1508w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/03/virgin-america1-177x300.png 177w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/03/virgin-america1-768x1301.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/03/virgin-america1-605x1024.png 605w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 425px) 100vw, 425px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/03/virgin-america2.png\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-432216\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-432216\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/03/virgin-america2.png\" alt=\"virgin america2\" width=\"425\" height=\"542\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/03/virgin-america2.png 1500w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/03/virgin-america2-235x300.png 235w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/03/virgin-america2-768x980.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/03/virgin-america2-803x1024.png 803w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 425px) 100vw, 425px\" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>躺枪的Virgin Australia脸书页面：</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/03/virgin-australia1.png\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-432215\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-432215\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/03/virgin-australia1.png\" alt=\"virgin australia1\" width=\"500\" height=\"167\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/03/virgin-australia1.png 1620w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/03/virgin-australia1-300x100.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/03/virgin-australia1-768x257.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/03/virgin-australia1-1024x343.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/03/virgin-australia-2.png\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-432214\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-432214\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/03/virgin-australia-2.png\" alt=\"virgin australia 2\" width=\"500\" height=\"159\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/03/virgin-australia-2.png 1612w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/03/virgin-australia-2-300x95.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/03/virgin-australia-2-768x244.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/03/virgin-australia-2-1024x325.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>维珍集团主页是重灾区：</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/03/Virgin-group.png\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-432218\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-432218\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/03/Virgin-group.png\" alt=\"Virgin group\" width=\"450\" height=\"5904\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/03/Virgin-group.png 496w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/03/Virgin-group-78x1024.png 78w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>附维珍集团旗下公司一览：</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/03/virgin-companies.png\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-432219\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-432219\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/03/virgin-companies.png\" alt=\"virgin companies\" width=\"500\" height=\"745\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/03/virgin-companies.png 1652w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/03/virgin-companies-201x300.png 201w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/03/virgin-companies-768x1144.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/03/virgin-companies-688x1024.png 688w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p>（维珍集团官网截图）</p>\n","author":980,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,27949],"tags":[25322,30038,30050,9481,22054]}